I think I got the same error when I had a typo in my serverless.json. Make sure you have defined “contacts” as endpoint in this file, for example?
```{
  "runtime": "nodejs12.x",
  "version": "1.0",
  "endpoints": {
    "contacts": {
      "method": "GET",
      "file": "contacts.js"
    }
  }
}```
